data.description: Experience the essence of home in this updated, 2 bedroom/2 full bath condo nestled in one of Sandy Springs' most coveted neighborhoods. Situated on the rear lower level, this corner unit offers tranquility with its private wooded view of the pond, all while being just minutes away from Sandy Springs City Center, Downtown Roswell, and major highways.  Step into the open and spacious floor plan, where the living room with gas fireplace welcomes you, flowing seamlessly into a beautiful sunroom and deck. The kitchen boasts granite countertops, white cabinets, and a full appliance package, perfect for culinary endeavors. Entertain effortlessly in the dining room adjacent to the kitchen.  With bedrooms strategically placed on opposite ends of the unit, enjoy the flexibility of a perfect roommate floorplan or a serene primary suite away from guests. Community amenities such as pool and tennis await, while nearby walking and nature trails along the Chattahoochee offer outdoor adventures.  Welcome home to Dunwoody Hills, where comfort meets convenience. Don't miss your chance to make this charming condo your own retreat in the heart of Sandy Springs.
